Package: GenomePal
Title: Create Genome Annotation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Haibo", "Liu", , "haibo.liu@umassmed.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4213-2883"))
Description: Create a BSgenome package from the genome sequences in a fasta
             file, and create OrgDb, geneAnnotation, and genomeAnnotation
             objects from a BSgenome, EnsDb, and GTF, which can be used for
             customized ArchR-based analyses.
